#ident	"@(#)bnu.admin:Helsys_r	1.4"

ABSTRACT:
	The remove task allows you to remove a system from the list of systems
	with which your system may initiate communication.
	
slistsys:System
	Give the node name of the system for which you want information.
	Give "All" to see information about every remote system.

srmsys:System
	Give the node name of the system that you no longer want to
	contact.  System information will be listed for your confirmation 
	before removal.

